<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Hospital</title>
    <style>
        /* General Styles */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #f3eaff, #d5bfff);
            color:#6A5ACD;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Header */
        header {
            background:#6A5ACD;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* About Section */
        .about-container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .about-container h2 {
            color: #6a0dad;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .about-container p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #4b0082;
        }

        /* Home Button */
        .home-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background:#6A5ACD;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .home-btn:hover {
            background: #4b0082;
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .about-container {
                margin: 20px;
                padding: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>About Our Hospital</header>

    <div class="about-container">
        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        <p>Our hospital is dedicated to providing world-class healthcare with cutting-edge technology and experienced professionals. We aim to serve our patients with compassion and excellence.</p>

        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>To improve the quality of life through patient-centered healthcare, innovation, and research. Our mission is to provide affordable and high-quality medical services to everyone.</p>

        <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
        <p>- Advanced medical facilities<br>
           - Highly experienced doctors and staff<br>
           - 24/7 emergency services<br>
           - Patient-friendly environment</p>

        <a href="/" class="home-btn">Go to Home</a>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
